videos.description: Golden State dominated Game 4 from the opening tip as the Warriors beat the Cavs by 23 to win the NBA Finals.

videos.description: Steve Kerr explains the challenges the Warriors faced en route to their third championship in four years and what Klay Thompson means to the team.

videos.headline: Kerr calls 2018 the 'hardest' of the three titles

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith explains how 'embarrassing' the Cavaliers looked in Game 4, saying even LeBron James looked like he quit on the team.
